<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You - AssistQR</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .thankyou-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
        }
        .thankyou-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .thankyou-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--success-color);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .thankyou-message {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-sm">
        <div class="thankyou-container">
            <div class="thankyou-icon">âœ…</div>
            <h1 class="thankyou-title">Thank You!</h1>
            <p class="thankyou-message">
                Your emergency report has been submitted successfully. 
                Emergency contacts for vehicle <strong><%= vehicleLicensePlate %></strong> 
                have been notified via email and SMS.
            </p>
            <p class="thankyou-message">
                <strong><%= notificationCount %></strong> emergency contact(s) have been alerted.
            </p>
            <div class="card" style="margin-top: 2rem; background-color: #d4edda; border: 1px solid var(--success-color);">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #155724;">
                    <strong>Your help matters!</strong> The vehicle owner and their emergency contacts have been immediately notified with all the information you provided.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

